libscope-guard-perl (0.03-2) unstable; urgency=low

  * debian/control: Added: Vcs-Svn field (source stanza); Vcs-Browser field
    (source stanza); Homepage field (source stanza). Removed: XS- Vcs-Svn
    fields. Add libtest-pod-perl and libtest-pod-coverage-perl to build
    dependencies. Add /me to Uploaders.
  * debian/rules:
    - delete /usr/lib/perl5 only if it exists (closes: #467853)
    - minor updates; don't install README any more (no additional
      information).
  * debian/watch: use dist-based URL.
  * debian/copyright: mention specific upstream source location.
  * Set Standards-Version to 3.7.3 (no changes).

